snippet.textDisplay:
The philosophy of this song is,
No matter what nation, what religion or what political affiliation we belong to at the end we are all human.
We came from the same place and end up the same place too and between this journey experience the same experiences of life and feel the same feelings but slightly influences by the culture. Life is too short to look for what makes us different instead of focusing on what makes us similar.
